description.en:
Airbloc Protocol redefines how data is collected, monetized and utilized. Leveraging blockchain technology and token economics, it seeks to facilitate more transparent data flows between data owners, data providers and data consumers. 

Ultimately, it aims to return data ownership back to data owners, provide applications with tools to collect and monetize data legitimately, and allow data consumers to purchase explicitly consented data with an auditable source of provenance for their business intelligence, research, and targeted marketing purposes.

ico_data.short_desc: Airbloc is a decentralized and transparent ad data trading network based on blockchain.

status_updates.description:
The Largest Credit Card Company in Korea — KB Kookmin Card Partners Us!

https://medium.com/airbloc/the-largest-credit-card-company-in-korea-kb-kookmin-card-partners-us-8afa4becd492

KB Kookmin Card’s ‘Future Nine’ program was created to discover, incubate and nurture promising companies with innovative technologies and business models. Out of the 323 companies that applied for the Future Nine program, Airbloc’s parent company, ab180, was selected as the top 10 technology companies in Korea that can use data related technologies and infrastructure to further improve KB Kookmin Card’s services.

Throughout the incubation and joint-business phase, KB Kookmin Card and ab180 will explore opportunities related to behavioural data analysis to further improve KB Kookmin Card’s services.

Airbloc's Q3-4 Development Progress and Codes Released on Github!

 (https://medium.com/airbloc/q3-4-development-progress-and-codes-released-on-github-38101de9088a)
✔️Data Management and Warehouse
✔️Identity Data Management
✔️Data Relay, Exchange and Export
✔️Aero Sidechain
✔️Airbloc Node

Vietnam's No.1 Social Marketing Technology Company YouNet Partners Airbloc 

(https://medium.com/airbloc/younet-vietnam-and-south-east-asias-leading-social-technology-marketing-company-partners-us-389b32428b57) 

✔️YouNet will distribute Airbloc's SDK to enterprises in Vietnam and Southeast Asia!
➕ More SEA enterprise partners!

Kakao’s Blockchain Subsidiary Project “Klaytn” Partners Airbloc Protocol

Klaytn is a global public blockchain platform developed by Ground X, the blockchain subsidiary of the leading South Korean mobile platform, Kakao.

https://medium.com/airbloc/kakaos-blockchain-project-klaytn-partners-airbloc-protocol-ee6d7014f75d

LINE's Blockchain Venture Fund, Unblock Ventures, Joined Airbloc As A Strategic Investor.

The inclusion of LINE’s blockchain venture fund further adds credence and legitimacy to Airbloc’s superior technology and drive towards mass adoption.

https://medium.com/airbloc/lines-blockchain-venture-fund-unblock-ventures-joined-airbloc-as-a-strategic-investor-c7ef8d8b3685

Japan and Taiwan's Leading Digital Advertising and Marketing Company D2C Partners Us

https://medium.com/airbloc/japan-and-taiwans-leading-digital-advertising-and-marketing-company-d2c-partners-us-5d48055cc147

D2C Inc. is a digital advertising and marketing company established as a joint enterprise between Japan’s largest telecommunications company NTT DoCoMo, Inc., Japan’s largest advertisement agency, Dentsu Inc., and NTT Advertising, Inc. on June 1, 2000.

D2C has a dominant digital marketing presence in Japan, China, Taiwan, India, Indonesia, Singapore and Thailand, and is already working with many of the leading enterprises in these countries with regards to digital advertising and marketing solutions.

Through this partnership with us, D2C will help Airbloc and Airbridge expand its presence into key markets such as Taiwan and Japan where there is remarkable growth in the prevalence and usage of mobile devices.
